PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Garbage Marketplace
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the garbage marketplace work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our garbage marketplace connects waste sellers with buyers. Users can list their recyclable or reusable waste items, and interested parties can purchase them for various purposes, promoting sustainability and reducing landfill waste.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of garbage can I sell or buy?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: You can trade a wide variety of items, including recyclables (paper, plastic, metal), compostable waste, electronic waste, and reusable materials. Always ensure items are clean and safe for handling.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is it safe to buy and sell garbage through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, we prioritize user safety. All users must verify their accounts, and we have guidelines for proper waste handling. We also offer an in-app messaging system and encourage safe meeting spots for exchanges.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I benefit from using the garbage marketplace?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: By using our app, you can earn money from your waste, find affordable materials for projects or recycling, reduce your environmental impact, and contribute to a circular economy. It's a win-win for your wallet and the planet!

HERO_SUBTITLE: Buy, sell, and trade unwanted items for a cleaner world and fuller wallet
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our trash-tastic marketplace? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What can I sell on the Garbage Marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: You can sell any unwanted items, recyclables, or literal garbage. One person's trash is another's treasure!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I list an item for sale?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply create an account, snap a photo of your garbage, set a price, and upload. It's that easy to turn your trash into cash!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is there a fee for using the Garbage Marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We charge a small commission on successful sales. Think of it as our garbage collection fee!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Sellers are responsible for shipping their garbage. We recommend using recycled packaging for an extra eco-friendly touch!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I receive an item that's too garbage-y?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Remember, you're buying garbage! But if an item doesn't match the description, contact our Trash Talk support team for assistance.
